To make the installer own tty1, ensure the live profile does NOT also start a
getty/agetty service on tty1. In artools dinit profiles the tty services are
usually named `tty1`..`tty6` under /etc/dinit.d. Either remove `tty1` from the
boot bundle, or add `installer` to the bundle and drop `tty1`. Verify with:
    dinitctl list
